docs.text: CDPHE SARS-CoV-2 This is the documentation for the Colorado Deparment of Public Health and Environment (CDPHE) SARS-CoV-2 workflows and tools. Next generation sequencing and bioinformatic and genomic analysis at CDPHE is not CLIA validated at this time. These workflows and their outputs are not to be used for diagnostic purposes and should only be used for public health action and surveillance purposes. CDPHE is not responsible for the incorrect or inappropriate use of these workflows or their results.
